arStrings.szText: Have you seen the Burned Knights that have come to Nahantu? I saw them a while back fighting Hollows. They were glorious...Oh, to be like them...
Chairul's voice trails off enchanted and mesmerized from the memory.
When I approached them asking if I could join them, they laughed me off. Claiming Iâ€™m unworthy and need to prove myself.
Well, I will. I have just the trial in mind, which is where you come in. As my witness.
"Which is where you come in" is said hopeful that the Player will say yes. Naive.
I can sense your doubt...Please, come with me and I will show you why this means so much to me.
